import React, { Component } from "react"; class Table extends Component { render() { const listItems= this.props.users.map((user) => {user.UserName} {user.FullNames} {user.Email} {user.Telephone} ); return (
this.props.onChange} className="table table-striped table-bordered table-hover dataTables-example" > {listItems}
userName FullNames Email Telephone
); } } export default Table;
